sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant CLI as pi CLI main
    participant Runtime as AgentSessionRuntime
    participant Session as AgentSession
    participant Agent as Agent
    participant Loop as agentLoop
    participant AI as pi-ai streamSimple
    participant Provider as LLM provider
    participant Tool as Built-in or extension tool
    participant Store as JSONL session store
    participant UI as TUI JSON or RPC mode

    User->>CLI: pi prompt or interactive input
    CLI->>Runtime: create cwd-bound services and session
    Runtime->>Session: bind mode and extensions
    Session->>Agent: prompt with expanded resources
    Agent->>Loop: run prompt with current state and queues
    Loop->>Store: emit user message events through session subscribers
    Loop->>AI: streamSimple(model, context, options)
    AI->>Provider: provider request and streaming response
    Provider-->>AI: text thinking tool-call events
    AI-->>Loop: assistant event stream
    Loop-->>UI: message_update events
    Loop->>Tool: execute validated tool calls
    Tool-->>Loop: tool result or error
    Loop->>Store: append assistant and tool-result entries
    Loop->>Session: turn_end and prepare next turn
    Session-->>UI: render or forward events
    Loop-->>Agent: agent_end when no queued work remains
    Agent-->>Session: settled state
    Session-->>User: visible response or protocol events
